1.title: Camping
1.plot: The Club heads into the great outdoors for a camping adventure! Brandon and Elainena trek through the woods spotting wildlife, while Chase and Daja fumble through their own canoeing experience. Back at the Fuel Lab, Chase discovers that breakfast can be healthy when he learns the secrets of the Breakfast in a Cup Recipe.

2.title: Sailing
2.plot: Daja hits the high seas for her first sailing lesson! From land to sea, she finds some freedom in learning how to rig and sail her own boat. Then, Brandon and Elainena bring the sweet and spicy in the Fuel Lab when they take on the Salsa Challenge. Elainena lends some flair to braiding crafts and Penny, the Outsider's mascot, with Project Paracord!!

3.title: BMX Biking
3.plot: Elainena's blown away when she hits up a BMX track. Experts show her a few tricks and tips for taking biking to the extreme. Back at the Fuel Lab, Daja has a hard time with a Veggie Pancake recipe that yes, includes actual vegetables. And Brandon decides the Club needs to chill... with their own pallet chair project!!

4.title: Longboarding
4.plot: Brandon longboards his way to stardom! Well, he really just gets an excellent primer in the basics from a longboarding expert. In the Fuel Lab, Daja and Chase whip out a few new ingredients to compete for the prize in the Power Pizza Challenge. Elainena joins the skating fun with a plan for a skateboard shelf project!

5.title: Surfing
5.plot: Chase gets gnarly and rips some waves! Surfing looks totally different when Chase hangs with an expert for a few pointers. Back at the Fuel Lab, one of Daja's favorite recipes gets a healthy makeover. Healthy Mac n' Cheese, anyone? She also brings some of the beach back from vacation for a shell wind chime project!

6.title: Horseback Riding
6.plot: Daja gallops into the unknown in a horseback riding adventure she's likely never to forget. Saddle up and get ready to shout a few "Yeehaw's!" Then things get a little cheesy in the Fuel Lab when Brandon and Elainena team up for the Scrambled Up Challenge. Chase and Daja take on their biggest, baddest project yet when they put up... a zipline!

7.title: Bass Fishing
7.plot: Brandon catches more than bass when he takes a trip through fishing basics with an Outsider expert. From bait to catch, there's more to fishing than catching fish. Then, Elainena gets fruity in the Fuel Lab with a fresh, healthy, homemade Popsicle recipe. She also teaches Brandon a new way to keep his catch... Gyotaku, the ancient art of fish rubbing!

8.title: Mud Walk
8.plot: Elainena gets the surprise of her life when Chase takes her on an extreme nature walk. Things might just get a little messy by the end. Then, the Fuel Lab hosts a competition that takes Elainena, Brandon, and Daja into the undiscovered world of smoothies... with avocados! Daja and Brandon also find out how catching some rays can get creative with their Sunlight Shirt Printing project.

9.title: The Florida Keys Aquarium Experience
9.plot: Chase dives in with some exotic fish friends at Aquarium Encounters in the Florida Keys! And boy, does he get up close and personal. Then it's off to the Fuel Lab where Brandon gets messy with a delicious No-Bake Granola recipe. Daja and Chase then dig into their own mess with a Travel Aquarium for Daja's friendly goldfish, Sunny.!

10.title: Herb Garden
10.plot: Daja discovers gardening with a group of adventurous students! Their school community garden has taken on a life of its own and she's there to check it out. Then, Chase and Brandon make salads interesting when they rush to the Fuel Lab for the Crazy Salad Challenge. And Chase keeps this episode green with a surprise Herb Garden project for his mom's birthday.

11.title: Bug Hunt
11.plot: Brandon discovers a whole new world... a tiny one! When he goes on a bug hunt, an Outsider expert shows him just how cool bugs can be. Then Chase races to the Fuel Lab for a twist on a stand-by after school snack, the Grilled Cheese. Meanwhile, Elainena and Brandon create their own Outsiders world when they put together a classic bottle ecosystem.

12.title: Keys Cable Park
12.plot: Chase balances on a fine wire when he drops in on the Keys Cable Park. Things get wild when he skims his way along the crazy cable system. Then Daja and Chase face-off in the Fuel Lab for a good ol' fashioned boys versus girls Sandwich Challenge, Master Class! And Daja surprises Chase with a personalized project: a reptile habitat for his new snake.

13.title: Favorite Moments
13.plot: The Club wraps up the season with a look back at some of their favorite Outsider moments. Some are fun, some are firsts, and some are just plain crazy! Then, Brandon conquers the Quesadilla and a new ingredient in a Fuel Lab experiment. The group also comes up with a plan to rid the club of mosquitoes by building a bat house!
